<p>How to user the template:</p>
<ol>
	<li>Follow the Link to the <a href="http://www.sec.gov/edgar.shtml">SEC Edgar Website</a>.</li>
	<li>From here you can search for the company you are trying to analyze.</li>
	<ul>
		<li>The easiest way is to use the stock indicator for the company.</li>
	</ul>
		<li>Once you have found hte company in question you will look for thei 10K filing for the most recent year.</li>
		<li>Use the information in the filing to fill out the template to the best of your ability.</li>
	<ul>
		<li>NO! THERE IS NO EASY WAY TO ACCESS THIS INFORMATION!</li>
		<li>Some companies may have an automated feed, but the SEC with whom all forms are filed does not offer any massive distribution that can be used.</li>
	</ul>
	<li>Once you have filled out the template, save the form taking care to leave it in CSV format and upload the file to the website.</li>
	<li>Being descriptive with your report name will assist the News Flash!</li>
</ol>
